Subject: rPSA-2008-0324-1 gvim vim vim-minimal

rPath Security Advisory: 2008-0324-1
Published: 2008-11-22
Products:
    rPath Appliance Platform Linux Service 1
    rPath Appliance Platform Linux Service 2
    rPath Linux 1
    rPath Linux 2

Rating: Minor
Exposure Level Classification:
    Indirect User Deterministic Unauthorized Access
Updated Versions:
    gvim=conary.rpath.com@rpl:1/6.3.90-2.7-1
    gvim=conary.rpath.com@rpl:2/7.2.040-0.1-1
    vim=conary.rpath.com@rpl:1/6.3.90-2.7-1
